{"tid":787602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搵貓義工想領養隻貓真係咁難？","createTime":"2018-08-20T19:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T15:05:04.000Z","uid":6847,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d44e4f6a33491d2c9e57585e444c35a92b56fcb1","tid":787602,"uid":6847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T19:38:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟都問左7-8個貓義工<br />\n唔係話比左人就係叫我等<br />\n等左4個星期都無消息<br />\n琴日再問一問佢<br />\n就話隻貓有人選<br />\n我只可做後備<br />\n屌.咁姐係玩鳩我姐<br />\n又叫人唔好去買<br />\n領養又比你地玩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n哎契弟咁<br />\n點撚樣叫人唔好去買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2200c3ac64eb00fbf2e32e7749434a5f0af44c22","tid":787602,"uid":6847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T19:40:31.000Z","msg":"又話想黎家訪<br />\n但講左成個星期都唔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1b895f3f9ef5e784e07d938eec8cfd19e2e5cc","tid":787602,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T15:05:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}